Abigail Balint - Final Project DACSS690V Spring 2024

Sidebar

Preparing the dashboard based on the instructions given at Magallanes Reyes (2022), and Aden-Buie et al. (2023).

You can find the code for this dashboard here: https://github.com/abbybalint/DACSS690V_AbigailBalint_Final

Column

Barplot - Work Location of Job Listings from Database

Histogram - Number of Jobs Available in Database by Listed Salary

Cat-Cat Bivariate Plot - Percentage of Jobs 2020-2024 that are Remote, Hybrid, vs In-Person

Map - Map of the World Plotting Calculated Average Salary for Data Science Jobs by Country

References

Source: “The Global AI, ML, Data Science Salary Index for 2024.” AI-Jobs, 2024, ai-jobs.net/salaries/2024/

Aden-Buie, Garrick, Carson Sievert, Richard Iannone, {\textbackslash}relax JJ Allaire, and Barbara Borges. 2023. Flexdashboard: R Markdown Format for Flexible Dashboards.
Magallanes Reyes, Jose Manuel. 2022. Data Visualization for Social and Policy Research: A Step-by-Step Approach Using r and Python. 1st ed. Cambridge University Press. https://doi.org/10.1017/9781108625425.
